Package statalign.model.subst.plugins

Class Summary
Blosum This class implements the classic Dayhoff substitution model.
CpRev This class implements the Chloroplast reversible substitution model, see also http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10795826
Dayhoff This class implements the classic Dayhoff substitution model.
Felsenstein81 This class implements the Felsenstein 1981 parameter model.
Felsenstein84 This class implements the Felsenstein 1984 parameter model.
HKY85 This class implements the HKY85 parameter model.
Jones This class implements the JTT (Jones-Taylor-Thornton) substitution model, see also http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/1633570
JukesCantor This class implements the Jukes-Cantor model for nucleic acids.
Kimura3 This class implements the Kimura 3 parameter model.
MtMam This class implements the mammalian mitochondrial substitution model, see also http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9732458
MtREV This class implements the reversible mitochondrial substitution model, see also http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/8642615
NucleotideModel This is the abstract class for nucleotide models.
NucleotideModelUtils This class implements various utility methods for nucleotide models.
ReversibleNucleotide This class implements the general time reversible parameter model.
RtREV This class implements the retrovirus substitution model, see also http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12165843
Tamura92 This class implements the Tamura 1992 model.
TamuraNei This class implements the Tamura-Nei parameter model.
Vt This class implements the Müller-Vingron substitution model, see also http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11382360
Wag This class implements the WAG (Whelan & Goldman model) substitution model, see also http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11319253
